a2t.text_actual: With Google Maps Street View, you can explore the world at street level. See popular landmarks, check out places you want to visit in your hometown or far away, and take a virtual trip around the world. To use Street View, open Google Maps, search for a place or long-press the map, and tap the Street View option. To learn more about Street View and see where it's available, visit maps.google.com/streetview.
